title: Top 100 NFL Players with Pete Prisco (Part 2) - Dak vs. Deshaun, Cook vs. Henry and more lingering questions (Football 5/21)
description:
Pete Prisco has defended the elite of his Top 100 NFL Players list (check out yesterday's pod in the feed for Part 1). Now it's time for him to further explain his sometimes curious placement of several players outside of the 25 best. Does Jalen Ramsey belong at 26? Is DeAndre Hopkins really the 4th-best wide receiver in football? Should Dak Prescott be ranked 16 spots ahead of Deshaun Watson? Prisco and host Will Brinson dive into the remaining questions from his list with plenty of debate and debunking.
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
